OL,7,FHannah Blythyn, the minister who is
OL,8,Fresponsible for fire services in
OL,9,FWales, will meet with North Wales Fire
OL,10,Fand Rescue Service this afternoon, as
OL,11,Fwell as Mid and West Fire and Rescue,
OL,12,Fto seek assurances that they've read
OL,13,Fthe recommendations of the Morris
OL,14,Freport.
