OL,7,FStuart Millington, who was until
OL,8,Frecently an assistant chief fire
OL,9,Fofficer in will be taken to an
OL,10,Femployment tribunal in Mold. He denies
OL,11,Fthe allegations.
OL,13,FITV Wales has been contacted by
OL,14,Fserving officers at both north and
OL,15,Fsouth Wales services who have
OL,16,Fexpressed their concern that Mr
OL,17,FMillington is not the right person to
OL,18,Ftake South Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,19,FService forward.
