OL,7,FMs Blythyn, the Deputy Minister for
OL,8,FSocial Partnership, announced earlier
OL,9,Fthis month the appointment of four
OL,10,Fcommissioners to oversee the service's
OL,11,Freform. They include former minister
OL,12,Ffor education, Kirsty Williams, and
OL,13,Fformer chief constable of North Wales
OL,14,FPolice, Carl Foulkes.
OL,16,FThey approved north Wales' assistant
OL,17,Fchief fire officer Mr Millington to
OL,18,Fbecome the interim chief on Friday, 9
OL,19,FFebruary.
