OL,7,FThe commissioners' brief according to
OL,8,Fthe , which has responsibilities for
OL,9,Fthe service, was to: "Establish and
OL,10,Foversee a new senior management team
OL,11,Fand related processes that are
OL,12,Funtainted by the failings identified
OL,13,Fin the report."
OL,15,FBut ITV Wales has discovered that Mr
OL,16,FMillington is himself being taken to
OL,17,Fan employment tribunal facing
OL,18,Fallegations of bullying by a member of
OL,19,Fstaff in his previous role as
OL,20,Fassistant chief fire officer at North
OL,21,FWales Fire and Rescue.
